### SmartCampus — fichier de requêtes manuelles (phase 9)
# 1. Lancer : uvicorn app.main:app --reload --port 8000
# 2. Login ci-dessous → copier access_token dans @token
# 3. Remplacer TOKEN par la valeur ou utiliser @token si extension REST Client

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@token = remplacer_apres_login

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Login admin démo
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@smartcampus.local",
  "password": "demo1234"
}

### Me (remplacer TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### ERP protégé — doit retourner 401 sans token
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/erp/status

### ERP protégé — avec token admin
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/erp/status
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### ERP — semestre actif
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/erp/semesters/active
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### ERP — liste étudiants
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/erp/students
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### ERP — étudiant par téléphone (agent)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/erp/students/by-phone/+243810000001
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### ERP — notes + moyenne
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/erp/students/1/grades
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### CRM protégé — status
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/crm/status
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### CRM — liste impayés
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/crm/payments?status=unpaid
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### CRM — solde Jean Mukendi (ETU-2026-001, id=1 après seed)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/crm/students/1/balance
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### CRM — paiements d'un étudiant
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/crm/students/1/payments
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### CRM — enregistrer paiement mock
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/crm/payments/1/record
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 100000,
  "method": "mobile_money",
  "reference": "MM-DEMO-001"
}

### CRM — relance
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/crm/relances
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_ids": [1],
  "channel": "whatsapp"
}

### CRM — communications
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/crm/communications?student_id=1
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Summary — fiche agrégée ERP+CRM (phase 7)
# Remplacer ID par l'id de Jean Mukendi après seed (souvent 10)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/students/10/summary
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Summary — par matricule via ERP puis summary
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/erp/students/by-phone/+243810000001
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

### Agent — health
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/agent/health

### Agent — moyenne (6.18)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "+243810000001",
  "message": "Quelle est ma moyenne du semestre ?"
}

